Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.72,0:00:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura is just Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.97,0:00:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And she'll always probably\Njust be Shimamura in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.81,0:00:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get it,\Nbut there's just a peace of mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.35,0:00:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Something that just gets my guard down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.14,0:00:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a wonderful thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.10,0:00:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.68,0:00:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you did show up again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.14,0:00:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And who might this be?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.93,0:00:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,She is {\i1}the {\i0}Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that even mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.39,0:00:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oho... So you're...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.14,0:00:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So, uh... What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.43,0:00:40.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike my foolish compatriot,\NI have come prepared with a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.06,0:00:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Please call me Yashiro Chikama.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.01,0:00:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I've come to Earth in search of my compatriot.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.51,0:00:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Compatriot...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.56,0:02:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Compatriot? Oh, compatriot. Like a friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.72,0:02:26.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, there's more of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Or rather, did you just say "Earth"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.43,0:02:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My compatriot came to this planet on a mission,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,but they haven't been back ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.35,0:02:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So I had no choice but to search for them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.22,0:02:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but it appears that I have landed\Nin the wrong location.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Alrighty, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You go ahead and enjoy talking\Nabout the unknown with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.35,0:02:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Aha! I sense some fishies over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.43,0:02:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sneaky, sneaky, sneak.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.51,0:02:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you, Hino. So the real reason\Nyou invited me fishing was...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.31,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hear that your name is Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.10,0:03:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear that you're so popular that all\Nthe locals come in droves to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:13.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm definitely not that Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.43,0:03:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, such modesty.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.22,0:03:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I have come from the future,\Nso I am not a local.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.43,0:03:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Just so we're clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, and I've come from the past.\NNice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be a typical earthling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.93,0:03:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.72,0:03:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you take that thing off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.56,0:03:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,My face is not quite ready,\Nso I do ask for your patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Is your face going to be delivered\Nfrom the bread factory or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be looking for your friend,\Nor rather, your compatriot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.64,0:03:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this something philosophical?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.35,0:03:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I have already confirmed\Nthat my compatriot is safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.14,0:03:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured I would take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.81,0:04:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So they contacted you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.89,0:04:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're able to contact each other,\Nyou can probably find each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,And there is a reason that we cannot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,--Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.22,0:04:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,--I-I see.\N--Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Plop.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't seem to get a bite.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important that you realize that first...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.06,0:04:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.14,0:04:28.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't seem to get a bite.\NThings aren't going as planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.10,0:04:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But that basically means\Nthat you've started something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.22,0:04:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You just felt like doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.89,0:04:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.47,0:04:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Heck yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,All we can do from here\Nis wish for a bright future,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and cast our lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.43,0:05:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So, yeah... That happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.10,0:05:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.64,0:05:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Was I that boring?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.14,0:05:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Could you not say it like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.18,0:05:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I was pretty busy\Nat work yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.06,0:05:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you have a part-time job\Nsomewhere? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.81,0:05:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.51,0:05:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.56,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Because you'd probably show up if I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're working is admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi once said that I was like a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.14,0:05:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I keep my distance from others\Nmakes me cat-like, apparently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.01,0:05:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Though there is a part of me\Nthat doesn't want to open up to people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,But Adachi's basically the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.43,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi dozing off with her head on my lap\Ndefinitely reminded me of a cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.14,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I think this is better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.68,0:06:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Because if I lay down this way,\NI can smell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.97,0:06:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Wait, do I have bad BO?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.43,0:06:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.14,0:06:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.18,0:06:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I think you lack elegance, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.64,0:06:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Elegance... Hm... Elegance, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.14,0:06:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think anyone's told me that before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.93,0:06:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.22,0:06:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna actually go to class\Nwith me this afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What brought that up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.31,0:06:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you know, attendance and such...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.76,0:06:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm saying is, it'd be more fun if we both\Nmade it as second-years together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it wouldn't hurt once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.93,0:07:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, hey... Let's go somewhere\Nonce classes are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.06,0:07:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have other plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.76,0:07:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Not today...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I never really do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.56,0:07:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll actually get a bite today.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.39,0:07:22.26,Default,,0,0,0,,School is its very own, unique society,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.26,0:07:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and if you brought that outside,\Nit confused things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.35,0:07:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm sure that some people would just\Nprefer to live out their lives at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, I want to catch a bright future.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,And for that to happen, I've got to\Ncast my line, or nothing will begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,How were your classes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.68,0:07:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Japanese history was fine, but I definitely\Ndon't understand math anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.56,0:07:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been to more classes than you and yet,\Nneither makes sense to me,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.06,0:07:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so where does that put me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.31,0:07:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You seemed to get a lot of attention, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm pretty sure you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.68,0:08:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it was you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably because you're so pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.06,0:08:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.72,0:08:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is the first time\Nanyone's ever called me pretty, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.26,0:08:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Your boy... friend\Ndoesn't call you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.64,0:08:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never had one.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.89,0:08:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... I guess everyone must be blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.01,0:08:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, where's your bike?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's out for repairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.10,0:08:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... So you actually\Nwalked to school. Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I thought you'd be here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.76,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.14,0:08:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.81,0:08:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to classes tomorrow, Shimamura?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm going to at least do my best\Nto go for more than three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.76,0:09:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you say, Miss Adachi?\NWhy don't we put in a little effort together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.06,0:09:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess... I can try a little harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Want a bite?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.81,0:09:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.93,0:09:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi? Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.39,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, there's some cream.\NThis is what you were waiting for, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.22,0:09:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Where should we go after we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Being with other people\Nseems to bring a little bit of pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.76,0:09:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not understanding something.\NSomething being a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.35,0:10:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Trying to mend relationships.\NPutting in effort to find solutions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.01,0:10:07.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes a bit of happiness is rolling\Naround in between all that negativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like when you're a kid and you find\Na tiny ball that you thought you'd lost,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:15.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to believe that\Nthe fact that I met Adachi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to bring me a brighter future.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.85,0:10:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's awkward, I'll let go! Like right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.39,0:10:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't awkward. You just startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I not then?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.76,0:10:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine. Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you like being coddled, Adachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.47,0:11:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Pedestrian-Vehicle Separated Signal"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorta surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.93,0:11:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.22,0:11:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,...that surprised...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shukoh... Shukoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.72,0:11:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.14,0:11:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw you here, so I thought I would say hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.47,0:11:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You really just walk around\Nin front of the station in that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.72,0:11:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is my finest outfit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I smell something exquisitely sweet\Nfrom your fingers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.97,0:11:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is quite nice. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.64,0:11:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably donuts, since I just ate some.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Donuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.35,0:11:52.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?\NThough I saw that coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a blip on my radar!\NThere're donuts in there, aren't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.14,0:12:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but don't grab at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.01,0:12:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give me one of those d-donuts,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall reveal one of\Nthe secrets of the universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.68,0:12:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? This is for my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.93,0:12:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--If they eat a donut, they'll take off\Ntheir helmet, and I can see their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--Poik.\N--If they eat a donut, they'll take off\Ntheir helmet, and I can see their face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, fine. You can have one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.39,0:12:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see... You can have this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so this is a donut.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:33.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Squeak, squeak, squeak, squeak...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Pshuu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.31,0:12:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're not taking off your helmet?!\N--Munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy, munchy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.18,0:12:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Munchy... Gulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.35,0:12:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Plop.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.64,0:12:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,--Yes, this was nice. It's very sweet!\NIt's oh so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.85,0:12:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,--You've never heard of donuts before?\NWhat kind of dance is that?\N--Yes, this was nice. It's very sweet!\NIt's oh so sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.14,0:12:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have any more sweets?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy some yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.85,0:12:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no money.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.81,0:13:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.10,0:13:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.81,0:13:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to get my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.18,0:13:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.68,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.51,0:13:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, was she mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.26,0:13:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like me to tell you what just happened
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.47,0:13:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of one of the universe's secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.51,0:13:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.64,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,She's mad because she didn't get a donut!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.76,0:13:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.93,0:13:27.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea if this self-proclaimed person
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.51,0:13:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,from the future is going to\Ngreatly change my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.60,0:13:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like things usually change your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.93,0:13:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Because no one knows what the future holds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.26,0:13:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.81,0:13:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, relationships are hard...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.76,0:13:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Shimamura thinks\NI'm prettier for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:14:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But she is greatly mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd say that Shimamura is way cuter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.31,0:14:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Her dreamy eyes, the way\Nshe modestly moves her lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.68,0:14:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My eyes keep looking at her face,\Nespecially her lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.47,0:14:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream where I kissed Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm into that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.10,0:14:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I just want to be closer\Nwith Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.85,0:14:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's definitely not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no deep meaning behind that kiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:00.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope! None!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.14,0:15:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying I'd never kiss her...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.97,0:15:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm not saying I absolutely want to, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.14,0:15:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If there was no one else within\Na 5-kilometer radius from Shimamura,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.51,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and she was in a deep sleep and an all-knowing\Ndeity just happened to reassure me
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.31,0:15:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,that she wasn't going to wake up\Nin the next 24 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe I'd get bored\Nafter 23 hours and I might
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.93,0:15:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,kiss her once to relieve some boredom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.18,0:15:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm definitely not that.\NI just want Shimamura to put me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.85,0:15:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want Shimamura to think of me first\Nwhen she hears the word "friend."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.93,0:15:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that may sound a bit possessive...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.22,0:15:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To be quite honest, I've been wondering
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,how much of a friend\NShimamura actually sees me as.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I just like her other friends?\NOr does she have other feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Sunday"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Am I just like her other friends?\NOr does she have other feelings for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcom--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.01,0:16:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.60,0:16:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you it was embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.14,0:16:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. It suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.06,0:16:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.76,0:16:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see them much anymore at our house\Nsince she entered high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.56,0:16:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.72,0:16:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oho... Are you two in the same class?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.89,0:16:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just order already.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.76,0:16:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have {\i1}tantanmen{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.14,0:16:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.39,0:16:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Shimamura\Ndoesn't really understand me,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.39,0:16:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but I could say the same about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't push me away when I rely on her,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.60,0:16:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but she doesn't try to rely on anyone herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That was how I saw Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.47,0:17:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you were finally shaping up,\Nand now look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.89,0:17:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's that supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our teacher. They were asking me\Nwhere you were like I'd be able to answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.81,0:17:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.26,0:17:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking about how cute\Nyou looked yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? B-But you're cute, too, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.81,0:17:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? It's not like I did anything.\NMaybe I'll go there to eat again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.64,0:17:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't. Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.06,0:17:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding. I'm not sure if I want\Nto go again with my family...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--It is sort of embarrassing\Nwhen you're with family--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.31,0:17:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--Hey, it's Shimamura!\N--It is sort of embarrassing\Nwhen you're with family--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.01,0:17:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Oh, so you did come.\NCan I sit next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.60,0:17:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.76,0:17:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... You're... Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.85,0:17:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Adachi! Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot her name but somehow\Nreally thought whispering would work?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.06,0:18:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.93,0:18:08.89,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's rare for you to eat school lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.60,0:18:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--I guess I don't hate this.\N--Well my dear {\i1}maman {\i0}slept in today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Their noisiness isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.56,0:18:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It reminded me of lunchtime in\Ngrade school and was a bit nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But it also felt like they were cutting\Ninto my time alone with Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.47,0:18:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't deny that I felt\Nthat this didn't feel right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, what are you going\Nto do about the afternoon?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.47,0:18:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I plan to go to class... I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.68,0:18:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.18,0:18:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,...could go to your house today.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.26,0:19:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.89,0:19:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home, Big... Sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.51,0:19:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.26,0:19:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. Oh, this is my friend. From yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.10,0:19:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.56,0:19:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.10,0:19:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a bit shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.85,0:19:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So your room's on the first floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sit wherever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.93,0:19:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.51,0:19:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Shimamura...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.47,0:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say it, don't say it, don't say it...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you mind if I sit...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.39,0:19:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:20:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Like... Between your legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What did I just say?!\NOh, my God. I'm a complete weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.76,0:20:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, it's okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.97,0:20:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, huh? I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.56,0:20:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.81,0:20:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a dream? Is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.97,0:20:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.81,0:20:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Shimamura's legs...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.85,0:20:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.01,0:20:31.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.43,0:20:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.39,0:20:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.10,0:20:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hello?! What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Well, my little sister likes\Nto sit like this. Isn't this normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.60,0:20:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah, sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.18,0:20:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's weird. It's super weird!\NMy clavicle hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.18,0:20:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--Um...\N--It's weird. It's super weird!\NMy clavicle hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.81,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,--What's up?\N--It's weird. It's super weird!\NMy clavicle hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,--Do you have a boyfriend?\N--Usually, people feel pain in their chest,\Nbut I'm feeling it in my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.35,0:20:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,--Do you think I have one?\N--Usually, people feel pain in their chest,\Nbut I'm feeling it in my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,--No...\N--Usually, people feel pain in their chest,\Nbut I'm feeling it in my bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.06,0:20:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,--You're right. Actually,\NI told you that the other day.\N--My bones start grinding so much\Nthat it feels like they're out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,--Did you?\N--My bones start grinding so much\Nthat it feels like they're out in the open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.60,0:21:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--Do you have one, Adachi?\N--I just want to relax...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.01,0:21:03.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.26,0:21:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.06,0:21:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And I immediately figured out
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,how to do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.51,0:21:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I like... you, I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.76,0:21:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, what?! What did I just try to say?\NDid I say it? Wait, did I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I think... I like you, Shimamura.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.47,0:21:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, I'm done for.\NI can't... I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.89,0:21:33.18,Default,,0,0,0,,This is... This is... This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.18,0:21:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I think I like you... Possibly, maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.76,0:21:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, like... really like...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.60,0:21:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a complete moron...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.72,0:21:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... You okay? Are you breathing?\NYour face is like bright red...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.51,0:22:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What the efffffff...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.97,0:22:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What the efffffff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 2: Adachi Question"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ow! Ow, ow... My neck hurts. It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 2: Adachi Question"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.56,0:22:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,--Ow! Ow, ow... My neck hurts. It hurts.\N--Even if the sun were to set and rise again,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Episode 2: Adachi Question"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.10,0:22:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,would tomorrow even come for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Isosceles Triangle'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Isosceles Triangle'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Adashimapedia: Aliens!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}"Next Time: 'Isosceles Triangle'"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We are aliens.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.01,0:23:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it weird for aliens\Nto call themselves "aliens"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.39,0:23:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's actually a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.56,0:24:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be more specific, like,\N"We are boobliens. Let us fondle your ti--"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.43,0:24:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to force you aliens outta here.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.35,0:24:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been defeated...
